room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: First time ever and was totally blown away! We did “kidnapping” and it was thrilling from beginning to end. Our gamemaster was Cat and she was awesome! She really helped heighten the experiance.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: My friends and I had a blast!! This was fun, exciting and a great escape room experience!! Cat was the best game master eve!! She had a great attitude from the beginning and very helpful!! We will definitely be back real soon..

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: Tons of fun and a much needed escape from the dinner/drinks/movie routine. We did a kidnapping themed escape. Lots of easy puzzles to keep you going that pieced together the bigger more difficult puzzle.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: The whole experience was fun and full of suspense. It was a great experience and I would definitely come back again. Our game master Ben was really nice and helpful. There was definitely a lot of thinking and some scares.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: I came with my daughters and nephews. We played the Kidnapping game. What a fun time we had! We did not escape so we can't wait to come back and try again. Great fun!
